r shift by solving intriguing puzzles. Become engrossed in this discerning horror puzzler.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Your watch starts now</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The graveyard shift awaits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete dynamic lighthouse tasks to keep the light alive</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whatever you do, do not let the light extinguish. Ships could crash. Or worse...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are responsible for the lighthouse from 12am to 6am</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive your shift to win</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/a6c2dc1c7a995529d170e65242b1787d.poster.avif?t=1727305679\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/a6c2dc1c7a995529d170e65242b1787d.webm?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/a6c2dc1c7a995529d170e65242b1787d.mp4?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/429083e1fc0b453cee4a6010e7cb7549.poster.avif?t=1727305679\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/429083e1fc0b453cee4a6010e7cb7549.webm?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321000/extras/429083e1fc0b453cee4a6010e7cb7549.mp4?t=1727305679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p clas